==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Haw-haw
<hw>Haw-haw"</hw> <pr>(h⟦add⟧*h⟦add⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Duplication of <ets>haw</ets> a hedge.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>See
<er>Ha-ha</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a loud laugh that sounds like a horse
neighing.</def> <wns>[wns=1]</wns>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hee-haw, horselaugh, ha-ha.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>a sunken fence (so as not to interfere with the
view).</def> <wns>[wns=3]</wns>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> haha.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hawhaw</ent>⟦br⟧
